summary: This document is an invoice from FedEx for shipping services provided to NYSG LLC. It details the charges incurred for a shipment, including transportation and handling fees, and outlines the payment terms and conditions.
keyFacts: The invoice number is 5-836-42540, dated May 11, 2001.
The invoice includes details about additional handling surcharges effective from April 16, 2001.
The payment is due by May 26, 2001.
The document mentions a shipment picked up on May 3, 2001, and delivered on May 7, 2001.
